commit message:
Create README.md

An Android app that uses the Open Weather Map (http://openweathermap.org/API) to display current weather conditions and weather forecast in selected world cities.The app is available for download at Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.haringeymobile.ukweather.

This is an Android Studio version of UK-Weather project.
